column5: Fishing lots of different areas these past few or so weeks. I havent even thought of taken pictures as I would just get them in and release quickly. This one I kept for a feed.  Back ground look familier Cliff ?
Great.  That spot is blown now!!!  Went out again this morning....still no steel or Browns....just pain in the #%! Chinooks!  Nice  fish Brian....I'm jealous. Lol
Need to get you up here, or me down there for a fish.
I think your spot is safe but feel free to PM it me Bri.  Nice avatar too.
What a coincidence!! I usually fish about 100m downstream from there!!!
I got this nice one in that spot!!!
